Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.14,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,130,,{\blur2}ら La ラ R ァ 羅 rA 乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.35,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}音楽の花を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.35,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,130,,{\blur2}ら La ラ R ァ 裸 rA 嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.58,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}千切ってはお星に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.31,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毒してあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.40,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呪縛なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.53,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}救済なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:37.33,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}(此処に)心、闇に捧げよ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:43.37,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…奇跡を日常に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:47.63,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…慈悲を与えましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:52.01,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}この右手あなたが掴むなら(果てなき)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:56.38,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}漆黒の(魅惑に)悦楽の(虜に)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:00.47,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}O…宿命は産声を上げる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:15.74,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}心臓と戯れた喜びから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.54,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}感じたのは生の息吹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:24.02,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今宵も心地よく深淵を揺らし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.08,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}あなたごと引き摺り込んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.96,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}秘密を導に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,130,,{\blur2}ら La ラ R ァ 羅 rA 乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.22,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}甘美な呪文が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.22,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,130,,{\blur2}ら La ラ R ァ 裸 rA 嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.38,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荊棘のように絡みついて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.14,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}離さないと言う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.46,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}躍るように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.50,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贖うように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:48.77,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}(此処で)歌と結ばれましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:52.98,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…仮面の民は誘う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.33,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…安らかな世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:01.57,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}あなたの過去を差し出すのなら(必ず)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:06.12,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}いかなる(願いも)いかなる(望みも)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:13.94,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sic…叶えてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:40.66,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…堕ちて、堕ちてゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.91,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…戻れない所まで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:49.21,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大丈夫　何も怖くないわ(委ねて)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:53.63,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}始めよう(永遠を)あなたと(私の…)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:57.86,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…奇跡を日常に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:02.22,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…慈悲を与えましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.60,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}この右手あなたが掴むなら(果てなき)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.98,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}漆黒の(魅惑に)悦楽の(虜に)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:15.74,IN_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}O…宿命は産声を上げる
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.39,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「欢迎来到 Ave Mujica 的世界」
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.62,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,75,,{\blur2}向着不可逆的生命历程
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.62,0:19:07.63,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}钉下终焉之桩
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.63,0:19:12.42,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}歪着头的人偶笑声空洞
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.76,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,75,,{\blur2}故事就由她们组成
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.76,0:19:20.14,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乘新月之舟
Comment: 1,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.14,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}La La La La La La Lan
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.35,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将音乐之花
Comment: 1,0:19:21.72,0:19:23.35,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}La La La La La La Lan
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.58,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}撕碎成无数片变为繁星
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.31,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}侵蚀你的内心
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.40,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是诅咒吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.53,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是救赎吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.53,0:19:37.33,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}于此处将心脏献于黑暗…！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.08,0:19:43.37,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…将奇迹变为日常
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.37,0:19:47.63,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…散播我们的慈悲
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.63,0:19:52.01,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若你牵起这只右手
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.01,0:19:56.38,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便会无尽沉溺于漆黑 愉悦无法自拔
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.38,0:20:00.47,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}O…新生的命运哭出第一声
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.36,0:20:15.74,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与心脏嬉戏得来的喜悦
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.54,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我感受到生命的气息
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.54,0:20:24.02,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今夜依然享受地摇动深渊
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.08,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将你也逐渐拖入深处
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.08,0:20:31.96,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟随秘密的引导
Comment: 1,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}La La La La La La Lan
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.22,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}甜美的咒语传来
Comment: 1,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.22,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}La La La La La La Lan
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.38,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如荆棘一般缠身
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.14,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说着不再松开
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.46,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如同舞蹈一样
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.50,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像赎罪一般
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.50,0:20:48.77,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让我们在此与歌结合
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.77,0:20:52.98,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…面具之人邀请
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.98,0:20:57.33,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…前往安宁世界
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.33,0:21:01.57,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要能献出你的过去
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.57,0:21:06.12,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不论什么念想 什么愿望
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.12,0:21:13.94,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Sic…我都会为你实现
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.95,0:21:40.66,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…堕落，不断堕落吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.66,0:21:44.91,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…直到没有归路的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.91,0:21:49.21,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系 没有什么好害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.21,0:21:53.63,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交给我吧 开启你与我的永远
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.63,0:21:57.86,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…将奇迹变为日常
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.86,0:22:02.22,IN_CH_EP13-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Ave Musica…散播我们的慈悲
